</b> (necrotic) ✦ <b>Recharge</b> when first bloodied</p><p><i>Trigger:</i> The sorcerer misses an enemy with an attack.</p><p><i>Effect (Free Action):</i> Enemies within 3 squares of the sorcerer take 15 necrotic damage, and the sorcerer rerolls the triggering attack roll.</p><p><i>Special:</i> At the start of any of its turns, the sorcerer can lose 25 hit points to recharge this power.</p></tr></td></table>",
